[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer run of the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` has detected a [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-based buffer overflow in the LittleCMS codebase. The overflow occurs during a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcall to `UnrollChunkyBytes` in `cmspack.c`, where a one-byte read goes beyond the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbounds of a locally allocated buffer. The crash is triggered through the [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcolor-profile transformation path, ultimately invoked by the fuzz harness in [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer.c`.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue: AddressSanitizer reports a stack-buffer-overflow [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in function[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes` at `src/lcms/src/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130:13[0m[39m`.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability Type: Stack-based buffer overflow.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Call Chain:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `CachedXFORM` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:537[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. `cmsDoTransform` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:206[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. `CreateNamedColorDevicelink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1103[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1210[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` in `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer.c`[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key Observations:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The overflow read targets address `[0m[1;36m0x7f8213960d24[0m[39m`, one byte past the end of [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe local array `i.i` in the stack frame of `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`src/lcms/src/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1185[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • ASan shadow memory indicates that the read lands in the redzone immediately [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter the buffer.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Local objects in the problematic frame include `i.i` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`dwFlags.addr`, `FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, and `LUT`. The variable `i.i` is of size [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut is read at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Investigation Scope:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Examine buffer size and indexing in `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Review data flow through `CachedXFORM` and `cmsDoTransform` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsxform.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Inspect the handling of local buffers in `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` and related [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdevice-link creation in `cmsvirt.c`.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzz harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m surfaces the issue but is not[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m:    stride.BytesPerPlaneIn = Size * [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1189[0m[39m:    int ColorSpaceBitsIn, ColorSpaceBitsOut;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1190[0m[39m:    _cmsTRANSFORM* xform = [0m[1;39m([0m[39m_cmsTRANSFORM*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m hTransform;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1191[0m[39m:    cmsPipeline* LUT = NULL;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1192[0m[39m:    cmsStage* mpe;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1193[0m[39m:    cmsContext ContextID = [0m[1;35mcmsGetTransformContextID[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhTransform[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1194[0m[39m:    const cmsAllowedLUT* AllowedLUT;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1195[0m[39m:    cmsTagSignature DestinationTag;[0m                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Issue Analysis and Root Cause Identification[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. The stack-buffer-overflow is triggered by `UnrollChunkyBytes` reading one [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbyte past the end of the `accum` buffer. The function expects to access `nChan + [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExtra` bytes but the provided “plane” buffer length only covers `Size * [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` bytes, where `PixelSize` undercounts `Extra` channels in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcertain chunky‐[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m formats.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In `cmsDoTransform`, `BytesPerPlaneIn` is computed as `Size * [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. If `PixelSize` excludes the “Extra” channel count, then[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor each pixel, `UnrollChunkyBytes` will read `nChan` bytes plus skip or read [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Extra` bytes, causing a one-byte overread when `Extra` > [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. The ASan report indicating a one-byte overflow on the stack frame of [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink` stems from an internal `cmsDoTransform` call during [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdevice-link creation. The frame-local buffer representing input pixel data is [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mundersized by exactly one byte relative to what `UnrollChunkyBytes` requires.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Targeted Fix: Correct PixelSize to include Extra channels[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Locate the implementation of `[0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `src/cmspack.c`. It must [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalculate total bytes per pixel for chunky formats as:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        PixelSize = NumberOfChannels + Extra[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      where[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        NumberOfChannels = [0m[1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        Extra             = [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      and for other formats [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., planar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, as per existing logic.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Modify `PixelSize` to add `Extra` unconditionally for chunky‐[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m formats:[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – If format denotes chunky [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e., NOT planar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, compute:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          PixelSize = nChan + Extra[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – Otherwise [0m[1;39m([0m[39mplanar, float[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, retain existing calculations.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Ensure `PixelSize` does not double-count Extra when T_SWAPFIRST or T_PREMUL [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflags are set—simply tally raw channel bytes.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Preserve Existing Behavior and Flags[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Do not modify the harness, fuzzing logic, or test code.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Retain `UnrollChunkyBytes`’ logic around `ExtraFirst`, `SwapFirst`, and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpremultiplication.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Confirm no upstream code relies on the previous, under-counting `PixelSize`.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Implementation Steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Open `src/cmspack.c`, locate `PixelSize` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlikely around top of file[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Add or adjust the logic for chunky formats:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt32Number [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number Format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            cmsUInt32Number nChan = [0m[1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            cmsUInt32Number Extra = [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mT_PLANAR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing planar logic[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m chunky logic[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                return nChan + Extra;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Run existing test suite and fuzz harness to verify no regressions.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Add a targeted unit test: call `cmsDoTransform` on a single-pixel buffer with[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[33mExtra[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., premultiplied alpha[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and confirm no buffer overflow.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – The overflow arises because the stride calculation omitted the Extra channel [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom total bytes per pixel.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – By fixing `PixelSize`, `BytesPerPlaneIn` and `BytesPerPlaneOut` are recomputed[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly, ensuring `UnrollChunkyBytes` always has enough data.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – This patch does not alter transform semantics or output, only buffer sizing.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Similar fixes exist in LittleCMS for planar formats where `PixelSize` includes[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mall channels; we align chunky logic with that pattern.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Side-Effects and Mitigation[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Potential slight increase in memory usage when transforming profiles with [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malpha channels; negligible [0m[1;39m([0m[39mone extra byte per pixel[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – No performance impact on formats without Extra channels.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Regression tests covering chunky‐[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m formats with and without alpha should pass [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munchanged, except now safely handling Extra channels.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Validation[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Re-run `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` under AddressSanitizer to confirm the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack overflow is gone.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Add regression test for `cmsDoTransform` on RGBA [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit inputs, verifying no [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mout-of-bounds reads under ASan.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mINFO:__main__:Running: docker run --privileged --shm-[0m[33msize[0m[39m=[0m[35m2g[0m[39m --platform linux/amd64[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--rm -i -e [0m[33mHELPER[0m[39m=[0m[3;92mTrue[0m[39m -e [0m[33mARCHITECTURE[0m[39m=[0m[35mx86_64[0m[39m -v [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/user/aixcc/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95mlcms[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mout[0m[39m -v [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmp7idqi_ru[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcms_virtual_profile_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer report from the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` run shows a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m called via [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsTransform2DeviceLink [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. A patch was attempted in cmsxform.c, adjusting[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`stride.BytesPerPlaneIn` and `stride.BytesPerPlaneOut` to include an extra term [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but subsequent fuzz runs still trigger the same overflow at the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame code locations.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Running the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` with a generated input causes [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAddressSanitizer to abort on a stack-buffer-overflow in the function [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow read is traced back through CachedXFORM [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsxform.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsDoTransform [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsxform.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and ultimately cmsTransform2DeviceLink [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The corrupted stack frame [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m contains several local [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobjects; the overflow occurs [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m bytes into that frame, just past a [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte local [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariable [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The sanitizer log pinpoints an out-of-bounds read of size [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m at the redzone [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mboundary.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Important Observations  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow arises on the stack, not in heap data.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The problematic read is inside the packing routine [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msuggesting that input or stride values allow it to walk off a buffer.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The local layout in cmsTransform2DeviceLink shows multiple small [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffers/structures [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`, `dwFlags.addr`, `FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, `LUT`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The harness simply feeds data into LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput; the overflow is [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeep in the color-management code, not in the fuzzer harness itself.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - File modified: `src/cmsxform.c` around the stride setup in CachedXFORM.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Original lines:  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     stride.BytesPerPlaneIn  = Size * [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     stride.BytesPerPlaneOut = Size * [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->OutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Patched lines:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```c[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     stride.BytesPerPlaneIn  = Size * [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  + [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     stride.BytesPerPlaneOut = Size * [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->OutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->OutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Objective: enlarge the per-plane stride by an extra term.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After rebuilding and re-running the fuzzer, the exact same [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow occurs at UnrollChunkyBytes, with identical stack-frame [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffsets and sanitizer output.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Post-Patch Log  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The AddressSanitizer backtrace and stack layout remain unchanged.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow still reads at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m in the cmsTransform2DeviceLink frame.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No new coverage or different failure location; the patch did not prevent the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Code Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `UnrollChunkyBytes` in `src/cmspack.c`: examine buffer setup and how it [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindexes the input or output pointers.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stride computation and use in `CachedXFORM` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`src/cmsxform.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: confirm that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBytesPerPlane and other stride fields match the actual buffer sizes expected [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdownstream.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`src/cmsvirt.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: inspect local allocations [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, `LUT`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for fixed-size arrays or small structs that may be [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverrun.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Macros/functions `[0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: understand what extra padding [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis needed for certain formats.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The chain from `cmsDoTransform` through `CreateNamedColorDevicelink`: spot any[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39massumptions about buffer lengths or packing alignment that could lead to [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moff-by-one.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo speculation on root causes or fixes is included. This report focuses on [0m         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1257[0m[39m:         DestinationTag = cmsSigAToB0Tag;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1258[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1259[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check if the profile/version can store the result[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1260[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdwFlags & cmsFLAGS_FORCE_CLUT[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1261[0m[39m:        AllowedLUT = NULL;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1262[0m[39m:    else[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1263[0m[39m:        AllowedLUT = [0m[1;35mFindCombination[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLUT, Version >= [0m[1;36m4.0[0m[39m, DestinationTag[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1264[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1265[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mAllowedLUT == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1266[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1267[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Try to optimize[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1268[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35m_cmsOptimizePipeline[0m[1;39m([0m[39mContextID, &LUT, xform ->RenderingIntent, &FrmIn,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m&FrmOut, &dwFlags[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1269[0m[39m:        AllowedLUT = [0m[1;35mFindCombination[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLUT, Version >= [0m[1;36m4.0[0m[39m, DestinationTag[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1270[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1271[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1272[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1273[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m If no way, then force CLUT that for sure can be written[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1274[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mAllowedLUT == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1275[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1276[0m[39m:        cmsStage* FirstStage;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1277[0m[39m:        cmsStage* LastStage;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1278[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1279[0m[39m:        dwFlags |= cmsFLAGS_FORCE_CLUT;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1280[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35m_cmsOptimizePipeline[0m[1;39m([0m[39mContextID, &LUT, xform ->RenderingIntent, &FrmIn,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m&FrmOut, &dwFlags[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1281[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1282[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Put identity curves if needed[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1283[0m[39m:        FirstStage = [0m[1;35mcmsPipelineGetPtrToFirstStage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLUT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1284[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mFirstStage != NULL && FirstStage ->Type != cmsSigCurveSetElemType[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1285[0m[39m:             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mcmsPipelineInsertStage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLUT, cmsAT_BEGIN, [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35m_cmsStageAllocIdentityCurves[0m[1;39m([0m[39mContextID, ChansIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1286[0m[39m:                 goto Error;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1287[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1288[0m[39m:        LastStage = [0m[1;35mcmsPipelineGetPtrToLastStage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLUT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1289[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLastStage != NULL && LastStage ->Type != cmsSigCurveSetElemType[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1290[0m[39m:             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mcmsPipelineInsertStage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLUT, cmsAT_END,   [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35m_cmsStageAllocIdentityCurves[0m[1;39m([0m[39mContextID, ChansOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1291[0m[39m:                 goto Error;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1292[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1293[0m[39m:        AllowedLUT = [0m[1;35mFindCombination[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLUT, Version >= [0m[1;36m4.0[0m[39m, DestinationTag[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1294[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1295[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1296[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Somethings is wrong[0m[33m...[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1297[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mAllowedLUT == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1298[0m[39m:        goto Error;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1299[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1300[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1301[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1302[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdwFlags & cmsFLAGS_8BITS_DEVICELINK[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1303[0m[39m:                     [0m[1;35mcmsPipelineSetSaveAs8bitsFlag[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLUT, TRUE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1304[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1305[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Tag profile with information[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1306[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mSetTextTags[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhProfile, L"devicelink"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m goto Error;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1307[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1308[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Store result[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1309[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mcmsWriteTag[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhProfile, DestinationTag, LUT[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m goto Error;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1310[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1311[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1312[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform -> InputColorant != NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1313[0m[39m:           if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mcmsWriteTag[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhProfile, cmsSigColorantTableTag, [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mxform->InputColorant[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m goto Error;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1314[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1315[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The AddressSanitizer overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes indicates that the [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mper‐plane input buffer lacks sufficient padding for the “Extra” bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimplied by the pixel format.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Our earlier patch in cmsxform.c correctly added T_EXTRA to BytesPerPlaneIn/Out[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor the CachedXFORM path, but the cmsTransform2DeviceLink code path [0m[1;39m([0m[39min cmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill builds its per‐plane stride solely from “bytes_per_channel × channels,” [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39momitting the Extra padding.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - As a result, UnrollChunkyBytes advances its `accum` pointer by `Extra` before [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand after unpacking, reading one byte past the redzone into adjacent locals [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.i[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtriggering the stack overflow.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Critical Logic to Preserve[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The logic in cmsTransform2DeviceLink that duplicates the LUT, sets up [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcolor‐space/formats [0m[1;39m([0m[39mFrmIn/FrmOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and calls the line‐stride transform must remain[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintact.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Downstream calls to cmsDoTransformLineStride rely on the four stride [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparameters: BytesPerLineIn, BytesPerLineOut, BytesPerPlaneIn, BytesPerPlaneOut. We [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmust preserve how PixelsPerLine and LineCount are passed.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Location and Strategy[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Edit `src/cmsvirt.c`, specifically inside the `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction just before the call to `cmsDoTransformLineStride` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround where `FrmIn` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `FrmOut` have been computed[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Compute the Extra padding from the transform’s original input/output formats:[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • `cmsUInt32Number ExtraIn  = [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • `cmsUInt32Number ExtraOut = [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform->OutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Calculate per‐plane strides including Extra:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • `cmsUInt32Number PlaneBytesIn  = ChansIn * [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + ExtraIn;`  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • `cmsUInt32Number PlaneBytesOut = ChansOut * [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + ExtraOut;`  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m([0m[39mHere, `ChansIn` and `ChansOut` are already computed via [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsChannelsOfColorSpace`.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace the old byte‐plane arguments in the call to [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mcmsDoTransformLineStride[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich likely were derived from the [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCHANNELS_SH macros[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with `PlaneBytesIn` and `PlaneBytesOut`.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Detailed Steps[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Open `src/cmsvirt.c` and locate the end of `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` where it[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvokes `cmsDoTransformLineStride` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter computing `FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, `ChansIn`, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ChansOut`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Add includes if not already present:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        #include [0m[32m"lcms2.h"[0m[39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m for T_EXTRA macro  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Immediately before the `cmsDoTransformLineStride` call, insert:[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Ensure per‐plane stride accounts for T_EXTRA padding[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt32Number ExtraIn   = [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt32Number ExtraOut  = [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform->OutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt32Number PlaneBytesIn  = ChansIn  * [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + ExtraIn;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt32Number PlaneBytesOut = ChansOut * [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + ExtraOut;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Modify the call signature:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransformLineStride[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhTransform,[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                 InputBuffer,[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                 OutputBuffer,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                 Width,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                 Height,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                 BytesPerLineIn,[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                 BytesPerLineOut,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                                [0m[35m/[0m[39m* old: derived from [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m*ChansIn *[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOldPlaneIn,[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                                [0m[35m/[0m[39m* old: derived similarly *[0m[35m/[0m[39m OldPlaneOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                                PlaneBytesIn,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                                PlaneBytesOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Remove or ignore the old variables used for plane‐bytes if they become [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munused.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Why This Fix Works[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach directly matches the buffer stride passed to UnrollChunkyBytes [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith its internal expectations: after unpacking the `nChan` channels, it will [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madvance `accum` by Extra bytes before or after the loop, and the caller has now [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreserved that space on the stack.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We do not alter harness code, tests, or external libraries—only the [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdevice‐link transform path in cmsvirt.c.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing logic for CachedXFORM [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpatched in cmsxform.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains effective; both[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode paths now consistently include T_EXTRA padding.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigations[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All pixel formats with non‐zero T_EXTRA will now consume slightly larger stack[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffers in cmsTransform2DeviceLink. Given that Extra ≤ [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m bytes and channels ≤ [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal extra bytes per plane ≤ [0m[1;36m112[0m[39m bytes—well within stack limits.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other code paths construct plane strides in cmsvirt.c, so this localized [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch is low‐risk.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We rely on ChansIn and ChansOut computed earlier; verify that these match [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to ensure consistency.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Regression & Testing[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` under AddressSanitizer to confirm the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow no longer occurs.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Execute existing unit tests for cmsTransform2DeviceLink to ensure no [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregressions in color conversion results.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. Relevant Code Ranges[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   <code_range>src/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1245[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1315[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>  [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfor context around the call [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto cmsDoTransformLineStride[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Stack after return:      f5[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Stack use after scope:   f8[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Global redzone:          f9[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Global init order:       f6[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Poisoned by user:        f7[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Container overflow:      fc[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
