[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Intra object redzone:    bb[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ASan internal:           fe[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Left alloca redzone:     ca[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Right alloca redzone:    cb[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m==[0m[1;36m18[0m[39m==ABORTING[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubprocess command returned a non-zero exit status: [0m[1;36m1[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mINFO:__main__:Running: docker run --privileged --shm-[0m[33msize[0m[39m=[0m[35m2g[0m[39m --platform linux/amd64[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--rm -i -e [0m[33mHELPER[0m[39m=[0m[3;92mTrue[0m[39m -e [0m[33mARCHITECTURE[0m[39m=[0m[35mx86_64[0m[39m -v [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/user/aixcc/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95mlcms[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mout[0m[39m -v [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmp7idqi_ru[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcms_virtual_profile_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is an AddressSanitizer-detected stack-buffer-overflow in the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLittleCMS library when running the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer`. The overflow [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs in `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m during a call chain from [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m through `cmsDoTransform` and related [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctions. A patch attempt was made that:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `cmsxform.c`, duplicated the transform call with added padding via `T_EXTRA`.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `cmsvirt.c`, replaced the loop over `cmsDoTransform` with a block computing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextra per-plane buffer sizes and invoking a stride-based transform [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`cmsDoTransformLineStride`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the code fails to compile with multiple errors—undefined [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstructure members, undeclared identifiers, misplaced braces and function [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdefinitions, and misuse of a `void*` as a structured type.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A fuzzing run with libFuzzer and AddressSanitizer reports a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read overflow [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `UnrollChunkyBytes` at cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[39m.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The call stack shows the overflow originates from `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsvirt.c, which allocates a small stack buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i` with only [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and then [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls into `CachedXFORM`, `cmsDoTransform`, and finally `UnrollChunkyBytes`.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The sanitizer output identifies the exact stack slot [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`, offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that was [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflowed and marks it with a redzone.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No assumptions are made about why the buffer is undersized, only that the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow happens due to reading one byte past the allocated stack slot.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **In `src/cmsxform.c`:**  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After the original `p->xform` call, the patch updates `stride.BytesPerPlaneIn`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `stride.BytesPerPlaneOut` to include extra padding [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mre-invokes `p->xform` with the new stride.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **In `src/cmsvirt.c`:**  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the loop that originally did `[0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, …[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, the patch [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwraps each iteration in a block that:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Computes extra bytes for input/output from `[0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform->OutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Calculates `PlaneBytesIn` and `PlaneBytesOut` using `ChansIn`, `ChansOut`, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand the extra bytes.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Calls a new function `cmsDoTransformLineStride` with the computed strides.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The patch also modifies error handling labels [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Error`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and frees.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Compilation Errors After Patch[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `xform` is treated as a structure but is of type `void*`, so `xform->InputFormat`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `xform->OutputFormat` fail.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Identifiers `ChansIn`, `ChansOut`, `hTransform`, `accum`, `wOut` are undeclared [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the patched scope.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Additional function definitions appear unexpectedly [0m[1;39m([0m[39merrors about not allowing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnested functions[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Unmatched braces lead to “expected [0m[32m'[0m[32m}[0m[32m'[0m[39m” errors.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A `goto Error;` statement refers to a label that no longer exists in the patched [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregion.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Recommended Investigation Areas[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo fully understand and address the overflow root cause, the following areas should[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe examined:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **cmspack.c, function `UnrollChunkyBytes`:**  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Analyze how buffer sizes are computed and whether the buffer on the caller’s [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack is correctly sized for all input formats.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **cmsvirt.c, function `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`:**  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Verify the dimensions and allocations of local arrays [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `i.i`, `FrmIn`, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`FrmOut`, `LUT`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and how they map to the transform’s requirements.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **cmsxform.c, stride calculations in `cmsDoTransform`:**  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Trace how `BytesPerPlaneIn` and `BytesPerPlaneOut` are derived from format [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdescriptors and whether padding macros like `T_EXTRA` are applied consistently.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Confirm that the input buffer and output buffer are allocated with sizes that [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatch the maximum expected data plus any padding requirements.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Definitions of macros/functions:**  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `T_EXTRA` macro and how format enumeration encodes extra channels.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `cmsDoTransformLineStride`, to ensure its parameters align with the intended [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory layout.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Otherwise, it is already correct for all formats[0m                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:192[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m207[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:void CMSEXPORT [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsHTRANSFORM  Transform,[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:                              const void* InputBuffer,[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:                              void* OutputBuffer,[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:                              cmsUInt32Number Size[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:    _cmsTRANSFORM* p = [0m[1;39m([0m[39m_cmsTRANSFORM*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Transform;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:    cmsStride stride;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m201[0m[39m:    stride.BytesPerLineIn = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Not used[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m202[0m[39m:    stride.BytesPerLineOut = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m:    stride.BytesPerPlaneIn = Size * [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m:    stride.BytesPerPlaneOut = Size * [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->OutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m205[0m[39m:           [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m:    p -> [0m[1;35mxform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, InputBuffer, OutputBuffer, Size, [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, &stride[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The AddressSanitizer report pinpoints a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte stack overflow in [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. That function always reads/writes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mT_CHANNELS + [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m bytes per sample, but its caller [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsDoTransform in cmsxform.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m only [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocates `Size * [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` bytes, where `PixelSize` returns _bytes per [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msample_ [0m[1;39m([0m[39mT_BYTES[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and ignores the number of channels and extra channels.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In named-color and device-link transforms, when [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmultiple channels[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the caller’s buffer is too small, so UnrollChunkyBytes walks [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moff the end.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix Strategy  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Modify the computation of per-plane buffer sizes in **cmsDoTransform** so [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat it truly reflects _bytes per pixel_ = T_BYTES * [0m[1;39m([0m[39mT_CHANNELS + T_EXTRA[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. This [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevents under-allocation of the stack buffer passed down to the xform routines.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Update the helper **PixelSize** in **cmsxform.c** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mused by cmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmultiply by channels+extra, so downstream callers automatically get correct [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstrides.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. _No changes_ to harness or test code. _No nested function hacks_ or misplaced[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbraces. _No reliance_ on cmsDoTransformLineStride. We leave existing function [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msignatures intact and preserve all transform logic.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Steps  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. In **src/cmsxform.c**, locate the static `PixelSize` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m175[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mChange it from returning just `[0m[1;35mT_BYTES[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to returning `[0m[1;35mT_BYTES[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, handling the double-size special case as [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. In **src/cmsxform.c**, verify that `[0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m200[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m207[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill calls `PixelSize` to build `BytesPerPlaneIn` and `BytesPerPlaneOut`. Because [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PixelSize` is now correct per pixel, no further edits are needed there.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Remove any previously attempted padding hacks [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe duplicated p->xform calls[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m— they are unnecessary once strides are correct.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Recompile and run the fuzzer + AddressSanitizer. Confirm the [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow no longer triggers in UnrollChunkyBytes.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Why This Works  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **UnrollChunkyBytes** always pads or skips `Extra = [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` bytes per sample. By sizing the caller buffer to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;39m([0m[39mchannels + extra[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * bytes/sample * Size`, we stop the overflow.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserves all existing transform internals [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cachedXFORM`, `cmsDoTransform`, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No regressions: all transforms still see the same total pixel memory layout, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mjust safer allocation.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance remains nearly identical [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma tiny additional multiply per stride [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msetup[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side-Effects & Mitigations  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Slightly larger stack frames in transforms that have non-zero T_EXTRA or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmulti-channel formats. Mitigation: this is unavoidable if we must be safe. The [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgrowth is minimal [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfew extra bytes per pixel[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If any external code incorrectly assumed `PixelSize` was “bytes per component”[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monly, this patch could change behavior; however, in LittleCMS the only use of [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PixelSize` in public code is in stride calculation. All packing/unpacking routines[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwork per pixel anyway.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References to Code Ranges  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   <code_range>src/cmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:175[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m186[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   <code_range>src/cmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:192[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m207[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA libFuzzer-driven test of the `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` uncovered a [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow in the LittleCMS codebase. The overflow occurs in the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when called from [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. A proposed patch modified the `PixelSize` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction in `cmsxform.c` to calculate per-pixel storage size by multiplying the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes-per-component by the total number of components [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchannels plus extras[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. After[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplying this patch, the same AddressSanitizer crash recurs at the same location, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the overflow was not resolved.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- When running `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` with a specially crafted input, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAddressSanitizer reports a stack-buffer-overflow in `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The backtrace shows the overflow originates from `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which allocates a local variable [0m[1;39m([0m[39midentified as `[0m[32m'i.i'[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m of length [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes but accesses up to byte offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack frame of `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` contains several local objects [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`dwFlags.addr`, `FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, `LUT`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but the overflow target is specifically[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe small buffer used to assemble the profiling data.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImportant Observations  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash is reproducible under libFuzzer with `-[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m`.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Sanitizer logs highlight a one-byte read beyond the stack allocation.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The problem surfaces during the chunk “unrolling” phase, after a cached color [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransform is generated.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No heap or global-memory issues are indicated; this is strictly a stack [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation problem.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- File modified: `src/cmsxform.c`.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Original function:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```c[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  cmsUInt32Number [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number Format[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      cmsUInt32Number fmt_bytes = [0m[1;35mT_BYTES[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m For double, the T_BYTES field is zero[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfmt_bytes == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt64Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Otherwise, it is already correct for all formats[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      return fmt_bytes;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Patched version adds calculation of total components:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```c[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  cmsUInt32Number [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt32Number Format[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      cmsUInt32Number fmt_bytes = [0m[1;35mT_BYTES[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      cmsUInt32Number channels = [0m[1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      cmsUInt32Number extra    = [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      cmsUInt32Number total_components = channels + extra;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m For double, the T_BYTES field is zero[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfmt_bytes == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt64Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * total_components;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Otherwise, multiply bytes per component by total components[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      return fmt_bytes * total_components;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The intention was to ensure pixel-size accounts for all channels and extras, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhoping to prevent out-of-bounds copying.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After rebuilding and rerunning the fuzzer, AddressSanitizer reports the exact [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame stack-buffer-overflow in `UnrollChunkyBytes`.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow remains at the same offset in the same call chain.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No change in crash signature or location—indicating the patch to `PixelSize` did [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot affect the vulnerable code path in `cmspack.c` or `cmsvirt.c`.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.c: around line [0m[1;36m130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: review the buffer size [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39massumptions and loop bounds.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlocal [0m[1;35mbuffer[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and how data is fed into `UnrollChunkyBytes`.  [0m             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransform profiles, ensuring they accommodate the maximum possible data length [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomputed upstream.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m544[0m[39m:                p->Lut->[0m[1;35mEval16Fn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn, wOut, p->Lut->Data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m545[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m546[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCache.CacheIn, wIn, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCache.CacheIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m547[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCache.CacheOut, wOut, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCache.CacheOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m548[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m549[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m550[0m[39m:            output = p->[0m[1;35mToOutput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, wOut, output, Stride->BytesPerPlaneOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m551[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m552[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m553[0m[39m:        strideIn += Stride->BytesPerLineIn;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m554[0m[39m:        strideOut += Stride->BytesPerLineOut;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m555[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m556[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m557[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m558[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m All those nice features together[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m559[0m[39m:static[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m560[0m[39m:void [0m[1;35mCachedXFORMGamutCheck[0m[1;39m([0m[39m_cmsTRANSFORM* p,[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m561[0m[39m:                           const void* in,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m562[0m[39m:                           void* out, [0m                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m564[0m[39m:                           cmsUInt32Number LineCount,[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m565[0m[39m:                           const cmsStride* Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m569[0m[39m:    cmsUInt16Number wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mcmsMAXCHANNELS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, wOut[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mcmsMAXCHANNELS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m570[0m[39m:    _cmsCACHE Cache;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m571[0m[39m:    size_t i, j, strideIn, strideOut;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m572[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m573[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35m_cmsHandleExtraChannels[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, in, out, PixelsPerLine, LineCount, Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m574[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m575[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Empty buffers for quick memcmp[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m576[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m577[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwOut, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m580[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&Cache, &p->Cache, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCache[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m162[0m[39m:#ifdef CMS_DONT_USE_FAST_FLOOR[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m163[0m[39m:    return [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;35mfloor[0m[1;39m([0m[39mval[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:#else[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m165[0m[39m:    const cmsFloat64Number _lcms_double2fixmagic = [0m[1;36m68719476736.0[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1.5[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m36[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1.5[0m[39m, [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m52[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m uses limited precision to floor[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m166[0m[39m:    union [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m167[0m[39m:        cmsFloat64Number val;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m168[0m[39m:        int halves[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m169[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m temp;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m170[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m171[0m[39m:    temp.val = val + _lcms_double2fixmagic;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m172[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m173[0m[39m:#ifdef CMS_USE_BIG_ENDIAN[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m174[0m[39m:    return temp.halves[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[39m >> [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:#else[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m176[0m[39m:    return temp.halves[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m >> [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m177[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m178[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m179[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m180[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m181[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Fast floor restricted to [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m..[0m[1;36m65535.0[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m182:c[0m[39mmsINLINE cmsUInt16Number [0m[1;35m_cmsQuickFloorWord[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsFloat64Number d[0m[1;39m)[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m183[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:    return [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;35m_cmsQuickFloor[0m[1;39m([0m[39md - [0m[1;36m32767.0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + 32767U;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Floor to word, taking care of saturation[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m188:c[0m[39mmsINLINE cmsUInt16Number [0m[1;35m_cmsQuickSaturateWord[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsFloat64Number d[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m189[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m190[0m[39m:    d += [0m[1;36m0.5[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39md <= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39md >= [0m[1;36m65535.0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:    return [0m[1;35m_cmsQuickFloorWord[0m[1;39m([0m[39md[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Test bed entry [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoints---------------------------------------------------------------[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:#define CMSCHECKPOINT CMSAPI[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Pthread support [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--------------------------------------------------------------------[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1096[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1104[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1096[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Make sure we have proper formatters[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1097[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1098[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1099[0m[39m:        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1096[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1104[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1096[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Make sure we have proper formatters[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1097[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1098[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1099[0m[39m:        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The AddressSanitizer report shows a one-byte read beyond the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte local [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariable “i” in cmsTransform2DeviceLink’s CreateNamedColorDevicelink loop.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - CreateNamedColorDevicelink calls  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     passing the address of a [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit integer as the pixel-input buffer. Internally,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibLCMS unpacks “accum” via UnrollChunkyBytes against the transform’s InputFormat, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich for named-color uses multiple bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes-per-component × channels[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunkyBytes walks over all input bytes, overrunning the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte integer on the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Prior attempts to fix PixelSize addressed output packing only, so the [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes remained.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix Strategy  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. In CreateNamedColorDevicelink [0m[1;39m([0m[39msrc/cmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, replace the loop that invokes [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsDoTransform with “&i” by code that:  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      a. Allocates a small, correctly-sized temporary buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor scalar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m matching [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe transform’s InputFormat [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes-per-component × channels[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      b. Fills that buffer with the named-color index [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in the expected raw [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrepresentation [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index for TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      c. Passes the address of this temporary buffer to cmsDoTransform.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Concretely, implement:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m before: [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, …[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cmsUInt16Number idx16 = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m i;  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &idx16, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This ensures the buffer pointed to by “accum” is at least [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe expected [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for named-color index[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, avoiding any read-past on the stack.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Preserve All Existing Logic  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - No other code paths or harness changes are needed.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - The call to cmsChangeBuffersFormat remains unchanged; only the argument to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsDoTransform is fixed.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - No external libraries, fuzz harness, or test code is modified.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Why This Works & Side-Effects  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - UnrollChunkyBytes reads out “Stride->BytesPerPlaneIn” bytes, which for [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed-color is a [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte per-pixel chunky format. By passing a cmsUInt16Number [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m rather than a [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte integer, we guarantee UnrollChunkyBytes’s reads stay [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min-bounds.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This does not alter any pipeline evaluation or caching logic, so the colorant [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconversion remains correct.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Buffer lifetime is safe: idx16 is on the stack but large enough for [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunkyBytes’s reads.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Minimal stack usage increase [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes vs. [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, negligible performance [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimpact.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Implementation Steps  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Open src/cmsvirt.c.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Locate CreateNamedColorDevicelink, around the loop at lines ~[0m[1;36m1099[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m1104[0m[39m.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Change:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
